  sectionId (44279)
  sectionNo (8)
  orderNo 8
  title Repealed.
  content `[Officers to answer in suits against them for acts done by order of superior authority.]—Rep. by Bombay Revenue Jurisdiction Act, 1880 (15 of 1880), s. 2.`
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_8_footnotes
